title: AVTECH Room Alert 3S: Sensor Power Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/avtech
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the power status of sensors
 connected to a AVTECH Room Alert 3S device.
 If power is detected the status is {OK} if
 no power can be detected the status is {CRIT}.

item:
 "Power State Sensor" if the connected sensor is a power sensor.

discovery:
 One service is created if the sensor emits power status data.
